ch.codebulb.lambdaomega

Class Promise<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.codebulb.lambdaomega.abstractions.OmegaObject
      • ch.codebulb.lambdaomega.Promise<T>

  • public class Promise<T>
extends OmegaObject
    A drop-in-replacement for CompletableFuture with a simplified, more concise API. It wraps around a CompletableFuture.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      static class  Promise.InterruptedException
      Contrary to the checked Exception InterruptedException originally thrown by CompletableFuture, a Promise will use this unchecked RuntimeException only.
